UI generation complete for Gmail Intelligence Hub.

Files modified:
- app/page.tsx: Complete single-file UI with 3 tabs (Inbox View, Follow-Up Hub, Settings)
- app/globals.css: Updated with Slate theme colors, glass-card utilities, gradient background

Features implemented:
1. Inbox View - Three-column layout with email list, thread reader, and copilot chat panel
2. Follow-Up Hub - Category filters, follow-up cards with actions, reminder date pickers
3. Settings - Gmail connection status, copilot tone settings, follow-up rules, schedule management
4. Sample data toggle with realistic demo data
5. Agent activity monitoring via useLyzrAgentEvents + AgentActivityPanel
6. Inline status messages (no toast/sonner)
7. Session-based multi-turn copilot conversations
8. Schedule management (pause/resume/trigger/logs) via @/lib/scheduler
9. Markdown rendering for agent responses
10. Full ErrorBoundary wrapping all content
